<plot>Universal Sigh explores those moments when one disconnects from reality - to decompress after a breakup, to calm nerves before a presentation, or to reflect on bad decisions. Through these moments, three isolated lives converge on a seemingly random city street, connecting to each other and reconnecting to the world around them.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?631072</url></doc>
